A. Because it hath the same manner of declining vvith Nostras, and Vestras;
                     Arpinas of Arpinum
                     ▪ and Rauennas of Rauenna, are so declined. like as all other Nounes that be Gentiles haue: and because it comes of Cuius, the Genitiue case of Qui, quae quod.
